i-saree-to-pair-with-shirt-blouse"/></a><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-92_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-94_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Image Credit: </span><a href="https://blog.mirraw.com/2019/02/27/10-latest-indo-western-style-blouse-ideas-for-saree/" target="_self">Mirraw</a>&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest iZvAhG pf-95_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-97_"><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);">#Tip 4: Cold Shoulder Blouses are Hit as anything</span><br></span></h3><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-98_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-100_">No this is true, it is not just for Sonam Kapoor or Piggy Chops - even you my dear patron can pair your traditional baluchari saree that you bought online the other day with an off shoulder blouse.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-avest iZvAhG pf-101_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-103_"><span style="color: rgb(208, 2, 27);">#Tip 5: And finally the Crop Top blouse</span><br></span></h3><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-104_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-106_">This is really going to come to the rescue if you can pair your baluchari with a lovely sequin woven crop top! I think it is nothing like a perfect combo, but you can call this one for sure!</span></p><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-gIBqdA biKLcv pf-107_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/43/assets/pf-f0ef746b-6271-48c4-8512-89beb4eeb217--rahmatstonecolorembroideredcroptoptealsilksareea0.jpg?6457" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1469/7362/t/43/assets/pf-f0ef746b-6271-48c4-8512-89beb4eeb217--rahmatstonecolorembroideredcroptoptealsilksareea0.jpg?6457 1536w" width="0" height="0" alt="crop-top-with-baluchari-silk-saree"/></div><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-108_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" cla